He made 227 competitive appearances, scoring 13 goals,<ref name=Irons/> became [[隊長_(足球)|隊長]] and was a member of the West Ham team which won the [[欧洲足联国际托托杯|欧洲足联国际托托杯]] in 1999.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportinglife.com/football/premiership/westham/reports/story_get.cgi?STORY_NAME=soccer/99/08/24/SOCCER_West_Ham_Nightlead.html&TEAMHD=westham&DIV=prem&TEAM=WEST--HAM&RH=West--Ham&PREV_SEASON=1998|title=Metz 1 West Ham 3 (Agg: 2-3)
